en.operator.description: Note! If you are going north of Arlanda, you also need an additional ticket which can be purchased in UL's app.
en.product.description: 10 day tickets to use whenever you want within 30 days. The perfect ticket for those who only travel certain days. The 30-day period will begin first when you activate the ticket. Activate it only on the day you want to travel.
en.product.description.long: Unlimited travel on any 10 days within a 30-day period. This ticket is for those who only travel certain days; for example, using public transport to get to work on some days and working from home other days.The 30-day period begins on the day the ticket is activated, so activate it only when you want to travel. A travel day extends between 00:00 and 04:30 the next day, i.e. a maximum of 28 hours and 30 minutes.If you are only going to make a single trip one day during your 30-day period, you can buy a single ticket for that particular trip and save an entire travel day for later.The ticket needs to be activated for the first time within 60 days of purchase. Once you activate your ticket, it can no longer be refunded.NOTE! For technical reasons, the ticket reader in the barrier or on the bus will display an incorrect validity period when you scan your ticket. The app always shows the correct validity period.
en.product.description.short: 10 daily tickets to use whenever within 30 days
en.product.title: 10/30 ticket

sv.operator.description: Obs! Ska du resa norr om Arlanda behövs även en tilläggsbiljett som kan köpas i UL:s app.
sv.product.description: 10 dagsbiljetter att använda när du vill inom 30 dagar. Den perfekta biljetten för dig som bara reser vissa dagar. Biljetten börjar gälla när du aktiverar den. Aktivera den först när du vill åka.
sv.product.description.long: 10 dagsbiljetter att använda när du vill inom 30 dagar. Biljetten för dig som bara reser vissa dagar, till exempel om du åker kollektivt till jobbet vissa dagar och jobbar hemma ibland.Biljetten börjar gälla när du aktiverar den. Aktivera den därför först när du vill åka. En resdag sträcker sig mellan klockan 00.00 till 04.30 dagen efter, alltså maximalt 28 timmar och 30 minuter.Om du bara ska göra en enstaka resa en dag under din 30-dagarsperiod kan du köpa en Enkelbiljett för just den resan och spara en hel resdag till senare.Biljetten behöver aktiveras första gången inom 60 dagar från köpet. Endast en biljett som aldrig har aktiverats återbetalas.OBS! Av tekniska skäl visar biljettläsaren i spärren eller på bussen fel giltighetstid när du blippar din biljett. Appen visar alltid rätt giltighetstid.
sv.product.description.short: 10 dagsbiljetter att använda fritt inom 30 dagar
sv.product.title: 10/30-Biljett

en.product.description: The perfect ticket for those who travel regularly and often. Travel as much as you want 30 days in a row. The 30-day period will begin first when you activate the ticket. Activate it only on the day you want to travel.
en.product.description.long: A ticket for those who travel regularly and often. Travel as much as you want for 30 days in a row. The 30 day period will begin on the day the ticket is activated, so activate it only when you want to travel.The ticket needs to be activated within 60 days of purchase. Once you activate your ticket, it can no longer be refunded.NOTE! For technical reasons, the ticket reader in the barrier or on the bus will display an incorrect validity period when you scan your ticket. The app always shows the correct validity period.
